Fix instructions (follow exactly; make targeted, minimal changes):
Consolidate the duplicated search-event behavioral tests. In `src/app/search-wrapper.test.ts`, remove the `describe('startApp search area events', ...)` block (lines ~197-383) which tests debounce, Enter, Escape, and clear-button click behaviors — these are ALL already covered by `src/app/toolbar-handlers.test.ts`'s `describe('search', ...)` and `describe('clearSearch', ...)` blocks. Keep only the `describe('startApp search area structure', ...)` block (DOM structure assertions) and the `describe('startApp search area: DomRefs unchanged', ...)` block in `search-wrapper.test.ts`, as those are unique. Also remove the overlapping 'does NOT render a Search button' test from `start-app.test.ts` since `search-wrapper.test.ts` already covers it. Run `npx vitest run` to confirm all behaviors remain tested after consolidation.

